{"tid":1013604,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"在美國也要見面 Jennie約會Irene","createTime":"2019-02-08T12:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T06:11:22.000Z","uid":74065,"like":36,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"fc992bd858a1d44845ba384de84edb999e80cdcd","tid":1013604,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:47:02.000Z","msg":"Red Velvet Irene和BLACKPINK Jennie兩位好閨蜜在台上總是形影不離的，令人十分羡慕她們的美好友誼。今個新年，更有人發現兩人同遊美國洛杉磯。<br />\n<br />\n網友於美國當地時間7日，在一間餐廳中發現Irene正舉著手機，疑似在調校些什麽，對面則坐著一個綁著髮髻的女生。不久，Jennie在Instagram上傳了幾張相片，成功解開疑團。<br />\n<br />\nJennie上載的相片中，顯示出與網友的目擊照一樣的餐廳裝潢，Jennie則一直對著鏡頭燦笑，旁邊更有Lisa呢！<br />\n<br />\n據知，Red Velvet日前剛完成在洛杉磯的演唱會，仍未離開。而BLACKPINK因為準備拍攝節目，成員都早早飛抵美國，順道享受假期。 Irene和Jennie看來因為同處洛杉磯，便相約出來用餐，把握每個見面的機會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/02/20190208_EN\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F02%2F20190208_EN&h=28c885ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vITTimA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvITTimA.jpg&h=2041c8d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3NSaQlJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3NSaQlJ.jpg&h=84b8931b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a9176a7f4180c486144e5e65e67e9bf44a9fe01","tid":1013604,"uid":174420,"like":154,"dislike":4,"score":150,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:48:32.000Z","msg":"爭埋單咁撚老套?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa7c0d32251da1d3985d98dec11167e964cc917","tid":1013604,"uid":74065,"like":11,"dislike":48,"score":-37,"quote":{"pid":"5a9176a7f4180c486144e5e65e67e9bf44a9fe01","tid":1013604,"uid":174420,"like":154,"dislike":4,"score":150,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T12:48:32.000Z","msg":"爭埋單咁撚老套?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime